Instagram and those beautiful polished pictures are just that: INSTAGRAM and don’t get me wrong I love it too and it’s part of my life; but just a LITTLE part of my life. I don’t wanna’ deceive you thats it’s all glitz and glamour. Example I’ve been sharing my anxiety and panic attack journey these 10 year on Insta and trust me ; its far away from those “perfectly” edited and styled pictures or events in which an increíble team makes me look effortlessly on fleek. It’s VERY challenging, these last 3 years maybe the most in my 12 years with general anxiety. Sometimes just getting out of bed is a huge accomplishment . So just sharing a bit of the bts, remember be kind we all have our battles. Have a great Monday.
————————————————————.
